elements.description: i want add suppliers with multipe data

steps.name: wait for username with "name" and "username" and "10"
Enter user name with "name" and "username" and "admin"
wait for Supplier link with "xpath" and "(//a[contains(text(),'Suppliers')])[2]" and "10"
Wait for AddIcon with "xpath" and "(//span[@data-caption='Add'])[1]" and "10"
wait for supplier number with "name" and "x_Supplier_Number" and "10"
Enter in "iam a new Supplier" with "xpath" and "//*[@id='x_Notes']"
wait for ConfirmOk button with "xpath" and "//button[normalize-space()='OK!']" and "10"
click Confirm ok button with "xpath" and "//button[normalize-space()='OK!']"
Wait for Alert ok button with "xpath" and "(//button[starts-with(text(),'OK')])[6]" and "10"
Click Alert ok button with "xpath" and "(//button[starts-with(text(),'OK')])[6]"
Click Logout link with "xpath" and "(//a[starts-with(text(),' Logout')])[2]"
